<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē kuṁbhbhitarkkakṣitiśaśigaṇitē mārgga
<lb n="2" break="no"/>śīrṣasya cuklē dvādaśyāṁ saumyavārē kamaṭhapu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>rapatērddarśasaijñōtsavāya <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ākalpaṁ māmi(ṁ)ḍaṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>mmā nijakulatilakaprōlamāyāstanūjā (<g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>)
<lb n="5"/>prādāddravyaṁ svakīyyaṁ svavrijanāharaṇaṁ vaiṣṇavā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>nāṁ sama<unclear>rpya</unclear> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śakavārṣaṁbulu 1168 Agunēṁṭṭi mārgga 
<lb n="7" break="no"/>śīrṣa śukla dvādaśiyu budhavāramunāṁḍu śrīkūrmmanāthu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>niki pratimāsamunā ĀmāvāsyaUtsavamu celluṭaku
<lb n="9"/>prōla<unclear>ma</unclear>mmakūṁttuṟu māmiḍiAmma śrīkūrmmadēvara śrībha
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁḍḍāramuna Oḍikina mallamāḍalu Ēnu Ī dharmmu
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vu śrīvaiṣṇavara[kṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g>]
